summary:
My name is Reneta Reinders and I was born in Bulgaria in 1987 and live in the Netherlands since 2011, married, two children. 

I feel comfortable being part of a team as well as working individually in a local or international environment.

Efficiency and expertise are very important to me and I am always open to new ideas and willing to learn.
